it is getting super difficult to even think about leaving for college. I dont want to grow up and i deffinitly dont think im ready to live on my own. i talk about how much i want it, but i dont think I can. Im not reasposible, i cry about nothing, i cant make myself any type of decent meal, when im sick i need to be babied and am totally unable to make myself better, I also have very little motivation and need someone constantly telling me what to do, i have little idea about whats wrong and right, and i think im gunna get into a lot of trouble being able to do whatever I want all the time. I might even DIE! (gross exageration) I just dont think im ready... for college, to move away from my friends, :( for highschool to be over, no more mommy, new people who i already know i hate, i just dont like change at all.
then agian i did do a lot of stupid shit...... that i regret

i hate it when people dont know about stuff but they judge people or things on there lack of knowledge. im not sure that made sense but it does to me. so 2 instances of this happening in my life in the past week. one time the first time it had nothing to do with me but i didnt like it. well this girl from my school who used to get beat up at her foster home ran away and then got put in an ambulence and everyone at school saw. well of course people start talking about it and changing and saying how this girl went crazy and blah blah blah. and changing what happened and saying she kicked the cop in the face and lots of bullshit that made me mad. I just felt so bad for the girl and I wanted to be able to help her so much. 
the second is a certain friend of everyone didnt attend a certain gathering that all of the guest were quite drunk at, and things happened being that all of those people were all drunk and i believe his exact words were "i semi wished i went, but i knew i would have vomitted all over myself if i saw what was going on" that just makes me super anrgy! so thats all.

so school is back to normal and its bad.
oh hey and im going to prom! woo me and d-bob are going together. probably. which should be classic, seeing as we've been friends since always. i cant really remember a time when i didnt know dan. i was pretty young when we became friends, its awesome. yeah that was a random tangent. all i can think about is how much i dont want to be in highschool anymore. oh yeha and my graduation party is June 25th all are invited. except for some people who we dont like. its nikki raphy chelsea and my grad party. should be sweet, cant wait. so spring break i hung out with the usual people and alysse, courtney, james, peter, andrew, Benji (hahaha) (bra theif)... so yeah i did alot too much to write about. but good times.

a side note... 
it may be that i just over react about everything but i fucking hate it when kristine has a boyfriend.. dont get me wrong i like him and i do want her to be happy but she never ever hangs out with me(selfish i know) if shes got a boyfriend.... until he breaks up with her and then of course im there for her. and this has always been the case, ever since she started dating jordan back when i was in like 9th grade. so ive decided not to call her anymore or make an effort to be her friend at all. because it totally seems like she doesnt care if we hang out or are friends. so im just going to give up. it sucks a lot... and im really sad just thinking about it, but thats just how it is... and it pisses me off a lot.. and i wanna chill with her and stuff but its like shes always with him, always on the phone with him, always having a conversation with him on text, or working or sleeping. so she doesnt have time for me or friends at all, and its like she doesnt notice or cares. at all.

so yesterday school started agian. it wasnt too bad i guess, i dont know i have a serious lack of motivation... i might not graduate.. oh well its like 1:00 and im finally going to school. so yup im a slacker..
